Code preview of the table CON_周期性固定费用模板

drop table "CON_PeriodTemplate" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_PeriodTemplate" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_PeriodTemplate"
(
"PeriodTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"RentTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CostCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"CostName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"FormulaCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"FormulaName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"ShoufuAccount" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"SettlementAccount" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"StandardType" INTEGER default 2 not null,
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(200),
"RightsType" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"ChargeShare" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"PriceWay" INTEGER not null,
"TermCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"TermName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"TaxType" VARCHAR2(10) not null,
"TaxGroup" VARCHAR2(10) not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_PERIODTEMPLATE primary key ("PeriodTemplateID")
);
